Dates
XML file with calendar that shows all events about to happen
- to it when you click on a date it highlights and shows all the events for that date
- when you click on an even it opens new Activity View
XML file - Date/event - shows when, where, with Who { name and profile pic }. Also feature: being able to ask if date is this going to happen
Button - we okay?
When clicked it starts a dialog/notification that ask the other user if the date is still happening. Two options yes and reschedule.
When clicked reschedule you choose to when or where.
If you want to be cancelled you can choose it, however if you cancellness more than 10 dates you get a time out.
